🔐 Modern Authentication System

A modern full-stack authentication system built using the MERN stack that demonstrates secure authentication techniques used in real-world applications.

The project implements JWT authentication, Google OAuth login, OTP email verification, and secure password reset workflows, while following best security practices such as password hashing, token-based authentication, HTTP-only cookies, and environment variable protection.

🚀 Features
🔑 Authentication

User Registration & Login

Password hashing using bcryptjs

JWT-based authentication

Authentication stored using HTTP-only cookies

Secure logout functionality

✉️ Email Verification

OTP-based email verification

OTP sent using Nodemailer

OTP expiration protection

🔁 Password Reset

Secure password reset via email OTP verification

Expiring OTP tokens

Encrypted password update

🌐 Google Authentication

Google OAuth login

Token verification using google-auth-library

Automatic account creation for new users

🔒 Security Practices

Password hashing with bcryptjs

JWT token authentication

HTTP-only cookies

CORS configuration for secure API access

Environment variable protection using dotenv

🎨 Frontend

Responsive UI built with React + TailwindCSS

Toast notifications using React Toastify

Client-side routing with React Router

API communication using Axios

